			rewards: [
				{id: "000B2001" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:source_gem" count: 8}
				{id: "000B2002" type: "xp" xp: 25}
			]
			title: "The Worn Notebook"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:worn_notebook"
			subtitle: "Your arcane education begins"
			description: [
				"В§6Ars NouveauВ§f is the magic system at the heart of this pack."
				"В§fThe Worn Notebook is your in-game guidebook вҖ” every recipe,"
				"В§fglyph, ritual, and familiar has an entry inside."
				""
				"В§eHow to get your Worn Notebook:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў Craft В§e1 Book + 1 LeatherВ§7 in any crafting grid (shapeless)."
				"В§7вҖў Or find one in dungeon chest loot."
				"В§7вҖў This quest's В§6starter rewardВ§7 gives you Source Gems вҖ” use them"
				"В§7  early to craft your first Source Jar."
				""
				"В§eHow to read the Worn Notebook:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў Right-click to open."
				"В§7вҖў Click a chapter header to expand it."
				"В§7вҖў Click any entry for full recipe details."
				"В§7вҖў Press В§eEscВ§7 or the close button to go back."
				""
				"В§ePriority reading order:В§r"
				"В§7  1. В§6SourceВ§7 вҖ” understand this before anything else."
				"В§7  2. В§6GlyphsВ§7 вҖ” how spell components combine."
				"В§7  3. В§6FamiliarsВ§7 вҖ” especially Starbuncle (powers Create in Ch 5!)."
				"В§7  4. В§6RitualsВ§7 вҖ” essential for mid-game automation."
				""
				"В§ePack adjustments you will not find in default guides:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў Apprentice Spellbook: В§e4 glyph slotsВ§7 (default is 3)."
				"В§7вҖў Mage Spellbook: В§e6 glyph slotsВ§7."
				"В§7вҖў Archmage Spellbook: В§e10 glyph slotsВ§7."
				"В§7вҖў Source cost multiplier: В§eГ—0.9В§7 вҖ” spells cost 10% less Source."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Gate quest: completing this unlocks all Chapter 1 quests."
			]
			dependencies: []
		}

		{
			x: -8.0d
			y: 4.0d
			id: "000B0002"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000B1002"
				type: "item"
				item: "ars_nouveau:source_gem"
				count: 16L
				consume_items: false
			}]
			rewards: [
				{id: "000B2003" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:source_jar" count: 2}
			]
			title: "First Source"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:source_gem"
			description: [
				"В§fSource is the magical energy that powers everything in Ars Nouveau."
				"В§fThink of it like electricity вҖ” you generate it, store it, and spend it."
				""
				"В§eWhat Source Gems are:В§r"
				"В§7Source Gems are compressed Source energy вҖ” physical tokens you"
				"В§7can carry, trade, and use as crafting ingredients."
				""
				"В§eHow to store Source:В§r"
				"В§7Craft a В§6Source JarВ§7 (Glass + Source Gem + Glass, bottom row)."
				"В§7Place it on the ground. Nearby magical plants and Starbuncles"
				"В§7will fill it automatically. Holds В§e10,000 SourceВ§7 per jar."
				""
				"В§eHow to SPEND Source:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў Casting spells draws from the nearest Source Jar in range."
				"В§7вҖў В§cIf no jar is nearby, spells cost your health!В§7"
				"В§7вҖў Always keep a Source Jar at base. Carry Source Gems when travelling."
				""
				"В§eEarly Source generation methods:В§r"
				"В§7  1. В§6Archwood TreesВ§7 (blue/purple/red bark) emit passive Source nearby."
				"В§7     Find them in magical biomes вҖ” use Nature's Compass to search."
				"В§7  2. В§6Source Berry BushesВ§7 near a Source Jar trickle Source in when ripe."
				"В§7     Harvest and throw Mana Berries near a jar to convert them."
				"В§7  3. В§6Starbuncle familiarВ§7 (Ch 1.2) auto-collects gems and fills jars."
				""
				"В§7This quest rewards 2 Source Jars вҖ” place them at your base immediately."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have 16 Source Gems in your inventory. They are not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0001"]
		}

		{
			x: -3.0d
			y: 4.0d
			id: "000B0003"
			tasks: [{
