			rewards: [
				{id: "000B2004" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:source_jar" count: 1}
				{id: "000B2005" type: "xp" xp: 20}
			]
			title: "Awakened Wood"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:archwood_log"
			description: [
				"В§fAwakened Wood is your first magical crafting material вҖ”"
				"В§fthe foundation of every Ars Nouveau device you will build."
				""
				"В§eWhere to find Archwood Trees:В§r"
				"В§7Archwood Trees generate in magical biomes with distinctly"
				"В§7coloured bark: В§bCascadingВ§7 (blue), В§eBlazinВ§7g (yellow),"
				"В§aFlourishingВ§7 (green), В§5VexingВ§7 (purple)."
				"В§7Use your В§6Nature's CompassВ§7 and search for 'ars_nouveau' to locate them."
				""
				"В§eHow to make Awakened Wood:В§r"
				"В§7  1. Collect В§6Archwood LogsВ§7 from any Archwood tree."
				"В§7  2. In a crafting grid: 1 Archwood Log вҶ’ В§dAwakened Wood LogВ§7"
				"В§7     (shapeless conversion вҖ” one log in any slot)."
				"В§7  3. Craft В§dAwakened Wood PlanksВ§7 from Awakened Logs (4 planks each)."
				""
				"В§eEssential items you will craft from Awakened Wood Planks:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6Source JarВ§7 вҖ” magical energy storage."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Scribe's TableВ§7 вҖ” where you learn glyphs from Glyph items."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Artefy TableВ§7 вҖ” where you inscribe spells into your spellbook."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Arcane CoreВ§7 вҖ” ingredient for mid-game devices."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Ritual BrazierВ§7 вҖ” the heart of every ritual setup."
				""
				"В§eTip:В§r В§7Bring Bone Meal on your first Archwood expedition."
				"В§7Speed-grow saplings into a full grove so you have a renewable supply."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have 16 Archwood Logs of any type. They are not consumed."
				"В§7(Cascading, Blazing, Flourishing, and Vexing logs all count.)"
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0001"]
		}

		{
			x: 3.0d
			y: 4.0d
			id: "000B0004"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000B1004"
				type: "item"
				item: "ars_nouveau:glyph_projectile"
				count: 1L
				consume_items: false
			}]
			rewards: [
				{id: "000B2006" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:glyph_harm" count: 1}
				{id: "000B2007" type: "xp" xp: 30}
			]
			title: "Your First Glyph"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:glyph_projectile"
			description: [
				"В§fGlyphs are the building blocks of every spell."
				"В§fA spell is a sequence of glyphs вҖ” like a sentence where each"
				"В§fword is a magical instruction."
				""
				"В§eThe three glyph types:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§bForm glyphsВ§7 вҖ” HOW the spell travels."
				"В§7  Examples: Projectile, Touch, AOE, Burst, Wave."
				"В§7вҖў В§aEffect glyphsВ§7 вҖ” WHAT the spell does."
				"В§7  Examples: Harm, Fire, Freeze, Heal, Light, Break."
				"В§7вҖў В§eAugment glyphsВ§7 вҖ” modifies the spell's behaviour."
				"В§7  Examples: Amplify, Extend Time, Pierce, Haste, Fortune."
				""
				"В§eHow to craft Glyphs:В§r"
				"В§7  1. Build an В§6ApparatusВ§7 (Awakened Wood Planks + Arcane Core pattern"
				"В§7     shown in the Worn Notebook вҶ’ Glyphs section)."
				"В§7  2. Place the Apparatus with a Source Jar nearby."
				"В§7  3. Put ingredients on the Apparatus pedestals as shown in JEI."
				"В§7  4. The Apparatus converts ingredients вҶ’ Glyph item using Source."
				""
				"В§eHow to LEARN a Glyph:В§r"
				"В§7  1. Craft a В§6Scribe's TableВ§7 (Awakened Wood Planks)."
				"В§7  2. Right-click the Scribe's Table holding your empty spellbook."
				"В§7  3. Drag the Glyph item from your inventory into the learning slot."
				"В§7  4. The glyph is permanently learned вҖ” the item is consumed."
				""
				"В§eStarter glyphs to prioritise:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§bProjectileВ§7 + В§aHarmВ§7 = basic ranged attack."
				"В§7вҖў В§bTouchВ§7 + В§aHealВ§7 = self or ally heal."
				"В§7вҖў В§bTouchВ§7 + В§aLightВ§7 = place a light source (no torches needed!)."
				""
				"В§7This quest rewards В§6Glyph: HarmВ§7 вҖ” combine it with Projectile."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have a Glyph: Projectile in your inventory. Not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0001"]
		}

		{
			x: -6.0d
			y: 8.0d
			id: "000B0005"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000B1005"
