			]
			title: "A Touch of Magic"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:apprentice_spellbook"
			description: [
				"В§fYou have Source. You have Awakened Wood. You have a glyph."
				"В§fTime to cast your first real spell."
				""
				"В§eCraft an Apprentice Spellbook:В§r"
				"В§7  Recipe: Awakened Wood Planks surrounding a Book + Source Gem"
				"В§7  (check JEI вҖ” search 'Apprentice Spellbook')."
				""
				"В§eBuild your first spell:В§r"
				"В§7  1. Craft a В§6Scribe's TableВ§7 from Awakened Wood Planks and place it."
				"В§7  2. Right-click the table while holding your Apprentice Spellbook."
				"В§7  3. In the В§6Glyph panelВ§7 on the left, click a Form glyph you have learned."
				"В§7  4. Click an Effect glyph to add it after the Form."
				"В§7  5. Give the spell a В§enameВ§7 and choose a В§ecolourВ§7."
				"В§7  6. Click В§6SaveВ§7 вҖ” the spell is inscribed into your book."
				""
				"В§eCasting:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў Equip the spellbook in your hand."
				"В§7вҖў В§eScrollВ§7 through your spell slots (up to 4 spells in this tier)."
				"В§7вҖў В§eRight-clickВ§7 to cast."
				"В§7вҖў Source is drawn from the nearest Source Jar in range."
				"В§7вҖў В§cNo jar nearby = costs your health. Build a Source Jar first!В§7"
				""
				"В§ePack note вҖ” spellbook slot counts:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6Apprentice:В§7 4 spells, 4 glyph slots each."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Mage:В§7 6 spells, 6 glyph slots вҖ” requires Create Brass (Ch 2.2)."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Archmage:В§7 10 spells, 10 glyph slots вҖ” requires End Portal Key (Ch 3)."
				""
				"В§7This quest rewards В§6Glyph: LightВ§7. Build В§bTouch + LightВ§7 as your first"
				"В§7utility spell вҖ” it lights your base for free, no torches needed."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have an Apprentice Spellbook in your inventory. Not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0002" "000B0003" "000B0004"]
		}

		{
			x: 0.0d
			y: 8.0d
			id: "000B0006"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000B1006"
				type: "item"
				item: "ars_nouveau:glyph_amplify"
				count: 1L
				consume_items: false
			}]
			rewards: [
				{id: "000B200A" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:glyph_pierce" count: 1}
				{id: "000B200B" type: "xp" xp: 40}
			]
			title: "Three Glyphs Deep"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:glyph_amplify"
			description: [
				"В§fOne glyph makes a spell. Three glyphs make a В§osystemВ§f."
				""
				"В§eAugment glyphs вҖ” the multiplier tier:В§r"
				"В§7An Augment glyph placed В§oafterВ§7 your Form + Effect changes the"
				"В§7spell's power, range, or behaviour without changing what it is."
				""
				"В§7вҖў В§eAmplifyВ§7 вҖ” increases damage or effect strength."
				"В§7вҖў В§eExtend TimeВ§7 вҖ” makes lasting effects last longer."
				"В§7вҖў В§ePierceВ§7 вҖ” projectile passes through first target and hits the next."
				"В§7вҖў В§eAOEВ§7 (as augment after Touch) вҖ” expands the effect area."
				"В§7вҖў В§eDelayВ§7 вҖ” spell effect triggers after a short pause."
				""
				"В§eExample three-glyph spells:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§bProjectileВ§7 + В§aHarmВ§7 + В§eAmplifyВ§7 = heavy bolt (great for bosses)."
				"В§7вҖў В§bTouchВ§7 + В§aHealВ§7 + В§eExtend TimeВ§7 = long regeneration pulse."
				"В§7вҖў В§bProjectileВ§7 + В§aFireВ§7 + В§eAOEВ§7 = fire spreads across a group of mobs."
				""
				"В§eWith 4 glyph slots (your Apprentice book):В§r"
				"В§7Form + Effect + Augment + Augment = double-modified spell."
				"В§7Try: В§bProjectileВ§7 + В§aHarmВ§7 + В§eAmplifyВ§7 + В§eAmplifyВ§7"
				"В§7вҶ’ Expensive but devastating. Two Amplifies stack multiplicatively."
				""
				"В§eSource cost scaling:В§r"
				"В§7A 4-glyph spell costs roughly 3Г— a 2-glyph spell."
				"В§7With this pack's Г—0.9 Source multiplier, 4-glyph spells are"
				"В§7still manageable if your Source Jar network is healthy."
				""
				"В§7This quest rewards В§6Glyph: PierceВ§7. Combine:"
				"В§7В§bProjectileВ§7 + В§aHarmВ§7 + В§eAmplifyВ§7 + В§ePierceВ§7 = long-range armour-piercing bolt."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have a Glyph: Amplify in your inventory. Not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0004"]
		}

