				{id: "000B200C" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:ritual_tablet_summon_starbuncle" count: 1}
				{id: "000B200D" type: "xp" xp: 35}
			]
			title: "The Ritual Circle"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:ritual_brazier"
			description: [
				"В§fRituals are large-scale magic that affect the world around you"
				"В§finstead of a single target. They require a circle of candles,"
				"В§fa Ritual Brazier, and a Ritual Tablet describing what to cast."
				""
				"В§eHow to build a Ritual Circle:В§r"
				"В§7  1. Craft a В§6Ritual BrazierВ§7 (Awakened Wood Planks + Source Gems"
				"В§7     in a pattern вҖ” see Worn Notebook вҶ’ Rituals for the exact recipe)."
				"В§7  2. Place the Brazier on flat ground at the centre of your chosen area."
				"В§7  3. Surround it with В§6CandlesВ§7 in the pattern shown on the Ritual Tablet."
				"В§7     (Each Tablet shows its own pattern. Candle colour does not matter.)"
				"В§7  4. Place the Ritual Tablet on the Brazier by right-clicking with it."
				"В§7  5. Right-click the Brazier with a В§6Source GemВ§7 to start the ritual."
				""
				"В§eSource cost:В§r"
				"В§7Rituals drain a significant amount of Source. Before any ritual:"
				"В§7  вҖў Have В§e3вҖ“4 full Source JarsВ§7 within range of the Brazier."
				"В§7  вҖў The Brazier draws from all jars in range simultaneously."
				"В§7  вҖў If Source runs out mid-ritual, the ritual fails вҖ” place more jars!"
				""
				"В§eRitual Tablets you will use most often:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6Ritual of Summon StarbuncleВ§7 вҖ” summons your first familiar."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Ritual of AwakeningВ§7 вҖ” converts Archwood into Awakened Archwood."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Ritual of FertilityВ§7 вҖ” instant-grows all crops in a wide radius."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Ritual of DisintegrationВ§7 вҖ” clears large areas of stone for mining."
				""
				"В§7This quest rewards a В§6Ritual Tablet: Summon StarbuncleВ§7."
				"В§7The Starbuncle is the most important familiar in the pack вҖ” it"
				"В§7auto-collects Source Gems AND powers Create machines in Ch 5."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have a Ritual Brazier in your inventory. Not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0001"]
		}

