			y: 12.0d
			id: "000B0008"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000B1008"
				type: "item"
				item: "ars_nouveau:imbuement_chamber"
				count: 1L
				consume_items: false
			}]
			rewards: [
				{id: "000B200E" type: "item" item: "ars_nouveau:relay" count: 4}
				{id: "000B200F" type: "xp" xp: 50}
			]
			title: "Source Network"
			icon: "ars_nouveau:imbuement_chamber"
			description: [
				"В§fA Source Network is an automated system that generates, transports,"
				"В§fand stores magical energy вҖ” so your spells never run dry mid-dungeon."
				""
				"В§eThe three layers of a Source Network:В§r"
				""
				"В§e1. Generation Layer:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6Source Berry BushesВ§7 near a Source Jar trickle passive Source in."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Archwood TreesВ§7 emit Source into nearby jars when close enough."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Starbuncle familiarВ§7 collects loose Source Gems and deposits them in jars."
				""
				"В§e2. Transport Layer:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6RelayВ§7 block вҖ” connects two Source Jars and transfers between them."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Mana RelayВ§7 вҖ” longer-range transfer, used to span your base."
				"В§7вҖў Chain multiple Relays to move Source from a farm area to a work area."
				""
				"В§e3. Consumption Layer:В§r"
				"В§7вҖў В§6Scribe's TableВ§7 вҖ” draws Source when you learn glyphs."
				"В§7вҖў В§6ApparatusВ§7 вҖ” draws Source when crafting glyphs."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Imbuement ChamberВ§7 вҖ” draws Source when infusing items."
				"В§7вҖў В§6Enchanting ApparatusВ§7 вҖ” draws Source for enchanting rituals."
				""
				"В§eThe Imbuement Chamber:В§r"
				"В§7The Imbuement Chamber is the crafting block where you create"
				"В§7high-tier Ars Nouveau items and imbue armour with magical properties."
				"В§7Recipe: Awakened Wood Planks + Source Gems pattern (see Worn Notebook)."
				""
				"В§eTip:В§r В§7Set up one high-density Archwood grove as your 'Source Farm'."
				"В§7Pipe its output via Relays to every workstation in your base."
				"В§7One Starbuncle patrolling a grove of 6+ Archwood Trees fills"
				"В§7a Source Jar in about 2 in-game hours passively."
				""
				"В§aв–ә Task: Have an Imbuement Chamber in your inventory. Not consumed."
			]
			dependencies: ["000B0005"]
		}

		{
